reviewText: i saw it. i liked it.  funny and piercing.  good job by the lead.  good job by the lead gal.  everyone did fine in this funny unusual film.  i know it landed with a thud -- but i think most people just don't get it.

A story of a loser who has been pampered all his life and is now trying to figure out who he wants to be and how to impress a whore.

It's just boring, it's not funny, there is no interest to keep you watching, and it goes no where.
